WEBVTT

00:00.265 --> 00:04.236
<font color="#fff00">Corrected & Synced by Bakugan</font>

00:04.238 --> 00:07.573
So... you broke in Lucia's house

00:07.575 --> 00:10.976
and you planted a... vase.

00:10.978 --> 00:14.446
And how is this supposed
to help Erik exactly?

00:14.448 --> 00:17.016
Well, if the police search her house...

00:17.018 --> 00:18.450
Oh, yes, the police.

00:18.452 --> 00:19.485
And did you think what will happen

00:19.487 --> 00:21.620
if they found out you did this?

00:21.622 --> 00:22.921
Well, they'd understand

00:22.923 --> 00:24.023
because we did it for a good reason.

00:24.025 --> 00:26.158
I understand that you want to help,

00:26.160 --> 00:28.193
but this isn't the way to go about it.

00:28.195 --> 00:29.595
Then what is?

00:29.597 --> 00:31.497
The best thing to do is to just...

00:31.499 --> 00:33.599
stay out of this.

00:33.601 --> 00:35.234
Look... Please.

00:35.236 --> 00:39.772
We will handle this. You can trust us.

00:39.774 --> 00:42.975
Uh, can I go to the bathroom real quick?

00:42.977 --> 00:44.943
I had about five glasses of O.J.

00:44.945 --> 00:47.479
Gotta get that vitamin "C"!

00:47.481 --> 00:51.884
And a glass of milk
for... calcium, yeah.

00:51.886 --> 00:53.719
And a glass of ginger ale

00:53.721 --> 00:56.255
for, uh... burping.

00:59.193 --> 01:00.459
Please?

01:00.461 --> 01:02.194
Fine!

01:02.196 --> 01:05.030
I'll be right back.

